                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Scalability",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": For applications with a large number of personalization records, the deletion operation could be resource-intensive. Consider batching deletions or archiving data before deletion if necessary."
